graph TD
    User[Cliente WhatsApp] -->|Mensaje / Selección| Webhook[Meta Webhook]
    Webhook -->|JSON Payload| FastAPI[FastAPI App]
    FastAPI -->|Extract message| WebhookRouter[Webhook Router]
    
    WebhookRouter -->|get_state| StateManager[State Manager]
    StateManager -->|ConversationState| WebhookRouter
    
    WebhookRouter -->|parse_intent| IntentParser[Intent Parser - Claude]
    IntentParser -->|Extract intent & slots| WebhookRouter
    
    WebhookRouter -->|update_state| StateManager
    
    WebhookRouter -->|Decisión de flujo| FlowBranch{¿Qué responder?}
    FlowBranch -->|Servicios| SendServices[WhatsApp Sender: send_service_list]
    FlowBranch -->|Horarios libres| CheckCalendar[Calendar Service: check_availability]
    FlowBranch -->|Texto Simple| SendText[WhatsApp Sender: send_text_message]
    
    CheckCalendar -->|Buscar libres| GoogleCalendarAPI[Google Calendar API]
    GoogleCalendarAPI -->|Slots libres| SendSlots[WhatsApp Sender: send_time_slots_list]
    
    User -->|Selecciona hora_xxx| InteractiveHour[Handler Selección Hora]
    InteractiveHour -->|Establece hora en estado| WebhookRouter
    
    WebhookRouter -->|Confirmar cita completa| GoogleCalendar[Calendar Service: create_calendar_event]
    GoogleCalendar -->|Crear Evento| GoogleCalendarAPI
    
    SendServices -->|Menú interactivo de servicios| User
    SendSlots -->|Lista interactiva de horarios| User
    SendText -->|Respuesta de Valentina| User

